{"tid":1593093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭若驊：希望日後有機會參與社區對話","createTime":"2019-09-25T02:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T04:00:57.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e25d7192e91f175fa6cb9b5b229c9638d22beb74","tid":1593093,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T02:12:07.000Z","msg":"律政司司長鄭若驊出發前往南韓前表示，曾經就反蒙面法作相關法律研究。至於會否推出反蒙面法，她說考慮因素很多，例如是否根據《緊急法》引入，對社會整體後果及效果等，至於是否由立法會通過反蒙面法，交由政策局考慮。<br />\n<br />\n政府明日舉行首場社區對話，鄭若驊表示，希望日後有機會參與，她希望對話是理性溝通，明日是個好開始，政府會不斷和市民溝通。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊今日前往首爾訪問，介紹香港現時情況，並推廣香港法律服務，將於星期四返港。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482434-20190925.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482434-20190925.htm&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9JuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=4c66e16b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482434-20190925.htm&h=2e5f11b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482434-20190925.htm</a>"},{"pid":"662aaabdc8d9e757bac786e4816d4d273b67a3ab","tid":1593093,"uid":41508,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T02:12:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbca7c7e0b67d51ab9798e67df9d9b6fe26c666a","tid":1593093,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T02:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"8e4f04894b7514e8e489ef2cc32efba400f4eaec","tid":1593093,"uid":15880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T02:13:00.000Z","msg":"留番入新屋嶺啦暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dadb6078cad9cbd409f905a7d316d